// Excel setup for the project

1. npm install
2. node testdata/createRegisterExcel.js
3. node testdata/createLoginExcel.js
4. npx playwright install
5. npx bddgen
6. npx playwright test

// Step 1: Run the creation script
        node testdata/createRegisterExcel.js
                ↓
        Creates registerData.xlsx in testdata/ folder

//Step 2: Run your tests
        npx playwright test "Register"
                ↓
        registerData.js opens registerData.xlsx
        reads the data automatically